{
  "page": "Karlon Stark",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/50px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/75px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/100px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Karlon Stark</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\"><img alt=\"House Karstark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/26/House_Karstark.svg/50px-House_Karstark.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/26/House_Karstark.svg/75px-House_Karstark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/26/House_Karstark.svg/100px-House_Karstark.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nKarl</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Karhold\" title=\"Lord of Karhold\">Lord of Karl's Hold</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark of Winterfell</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">House Stark of Karl's Hold</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Karlon Stark</b> was a younger son of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>. He was the first Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Karhold\" title=\"Karhold\">Karl's Hold</a> and the founder of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">House Karstark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlon_Stark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>About thousand years ago (possibly before 700 BC)<sup id=\"cite_ref-date_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-date-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> after putting down a rebel lord, Karlon was granted lands for his success and bravery. Originally the castle he built was named Karl's Hold but eventually the name changed to <a href=\"/index.php/Karhold\" title=\"Karhold\">Karhold</a> and the Karhold Starks became the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">Karstarks</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlon_Stark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-date-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-date_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a> recalls that <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlon Stark</a> put down a rebel lord \"a thousand years ago\"  (<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_20\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 20\">Catelyn III</a>). It is unknown if this means one thousand years ago (seven hundred years before <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>) or if <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> is being figurative. Martin has also said the Karstarks were founded \"more than a thousand years ago.\" (<a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/Asshai.com_Interview_in_Barcelona/\">Asshai.com Interview in Barcelona</a>, July 28, 2012)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlon_Stark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_20\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 20\">Chapter 20</a>, Catelyn III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>New title</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>1st <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Karhold\" title=\"Lord of Karhold\">Lord of Karl's Hold</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Karstark\" title=\"Rickard Karstark\">Rickard Karstark</a> </b><br /><small><i><b>as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Karhold\" title=\"Lord of Karhold\">Lord of Karhold</a> </b></i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404012504\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.083 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.274 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 751/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12971/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7161/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1277/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1697/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  262.6